messages.message: Doc summarization app takes quite a while, 20 page document has not completed yet after a few minutes. The `bulk_status` endpoint has been saying 0 cur_progress after 5 minutes still.

*Latency* after hitting RETURN in chat which prevents quick fire question asking. For example, if you immediately try to asking questions in quick succession, the system freezes to process the question instead of leaving the chatbox open to continue typing/quereying
